Show HN: Centralized Logging Tool
text:
It displays a list of log records of which you have inserted with:

curl "http://logs.thirdplace.no/log?token=hunterhn&message=here_is..."

One application is to insert log record from a cronjob to gain confidence that it is running properly.

source code: https://git.sr.ht/~thirdplace/logs/tree

Ask HN: ML to Address Ecological Problems?
text: Does anyone know of any companies that are working to apply ML techniques to real world problems like ecological/biological/geological engineering? Weather prediction I think is a good example but I'm thinking more along the lines of novel materials and plant cultivars for addressing issues from global warming like droughts and food shortages.

Ask HN: Have you ever heard of users demostrating against software?
text: Today in Trondheim, Norway, around 100 health doctors & nurses demostrated by walking with torches trough the city against the implementation of a new software in the hospital. The Helseplatform is an adaptation of Epic to the Norwegian Health system. Have this ever happen in history before? How bad can something be that users go out in the street to demostrate?
